A Quiz covering the diverse topics of Music, Entertainment, Literature and Arts. Join us for the event as we engage in a battle between minds over the genre of MELA. Explore the diverse realms of human creativity and passion in this quiz encompassing Music, Entertainment, Literature, Arts.. 
Test your knowledge across cultural dimensions, from identifying iconic melodies and literary masterpieces to recognizing celebrated works of art.
Dive into the MELA Quiz: Explore the world of Music, Entertainment, Literature, and Arts!
